sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Airflow as Airflow Scheduler
  participant NestAPI as NestJS Internal API
  participant SparkOp as Spark Operator
  participant Driver as Spark Driver Pod
  participant Crypto as CryptoService
  participant Executors as Spark Executors
  participant Source as Source DB
  participant Delta as Delta Lake

  Airflow->>NestAPI: GET /internal/pipelines/active
  NestAPI-->>Airflow: active pipelines
  Airflow->>Airflow: build DAGs in memory

  Airflow->>SparkOp: submit SparkApplication
  SparkOp->>Driver: start driver pod

  Driver->>NestAPI: GET /internal/pipelines/{id}/runtime-config
  NestAPI->>Crypto: decrypt credentials
  Crypto-->>NestAPI: plaintext secrets
  NestAPI-->>Driver: runtime config + creds

  Driver->>SparkOp: request executors
  SparkOp->>Executors: start pods
  Executors->>Source: extract data
  Executors->>Delta: write Delta
  Executors-->>Driver: complete
  Driver-->>SparkOp: exit success
